         <abstract id="aspace_24f260823b22824ab73c33ec52c68230">The records consist of correspondence, clippings, minutes of meetings, a scrapbook, questionnaires, exhibition materials, published materials, and notes documenting the Jared Eliot Association, with an emphasis on its "Great Books" exhibition.</abstract>
